node.title: Jetstar pilot Greg Lynn charged with murder of campers Russell Hill and Carol Clay
node.alt: A composite image of a man outside and a woman holding a glass of wine at a restaurant
node.description: Jetstar pilot Greg Lynn has been charged with murder after spending several days being questioned by police over the disappearance of campers Russell Hill and Carol Clay.
node.content: ["Jetstar pilot Greg Lynn has been charged with murder after spending several\u00a0days\u00a0being questioned by police over the disappearance of campers of Russell Hill and Carol Clay.", "Victoria Police Crime Command Assistant Commissioner Bob Hill said Mr\u00a0Lynn would appear in the Sale Magistrates' Court on Friday morning.\u00a0", "\"We are hoping this arrest brings us a step closer to providing the answers the families have been desperately seeking and richly deserve,\" he said.\u00a0", "More to come"]
